mcqs.question:
What is the time complexity of the following code snippet?

for (int i = 1; i <= n; i++) {
    for (int j = 1; j <= i; j++) {
        printf("%d ", i*j);
    }
}

What is the time complexity of the following algorithm that finds the minimum and maximum element in an unsorted array using a single pass?

min = arr[0]; max = arr[0];
for (i = 1; i < n; i++) {
    if (arr[i] < min) min = arr[i];
    if (arr[i] > max) max = arr[i];
}
